			act 'Be a smart ass.':
				*clr & cla
				demerits +=5
				grupvalue[1] +=3
				grupvalue[4] +=3
				grupvalue[3] -=3
				'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/bored.jpg"></center>'
				'"Of course. Please continue your super-fascinating lesson. Just keep it a bit up-beat please. If you talk any slower, I might fall asleep!" you answer boldly.'
				'The whole class bursts into loud laughter, and Mrs. Sokoloff has a rough time getting everyone to quiet down.'
				'"Miss <<$pcs_lastname>>, get out of class! Report to the Principal now!"'
				act 'Don''t leave the classroom':
					*clr & cla
					demerits +=5
					grupvalue[4] +=5
					grupvalue[3] -=5
					'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/bitchflip.jpg"></center>'
					'"What good would that do? Are you trying to get me to start smoking to pass the time? I''m not interrupting your classes, just leave me alone. I''m having some... girl problems. Would you like me to talk about those instead?" you answer brashly, not having any intentions of getting up.'
					'Your teacher just shakes her head, and after a while just decides to continue her classes. Obviously, you don''t learn anything today. You hear one of the boys behind you mutter you being a bitch, you turn around and flip him off.'
					act 'Wait for the end of the lesson': gt 'gschool_lessons', 'short_break'
				end
				act 'Go to principal''s office': demerit += 10+school_bunk*5 & gt 'gschool_office', 'principal'
			end
			act 'Reluctantly pay attention':
				*clr & cla
				'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/bathroom/angryteacher.jpg"></center>'
				'The eyes of Mrs. Sokoloff grow narrower, and even though you roll your eyes at her, you sit through the rest of the lesson in silence, at least pretending to pay attention sometimes. You don''t learn anything today, though.'
				act 'Wait for the end of the lesson': gs 'gschool_lessonsev2', 'geography'
			end
			act'Try to focus on the lesson':
				*clr & cla
				grupvalue[4] -=5
				grupvalue[3] +=5
				'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/attention.jpg"></center>'
				'You don''t want to get in trouble so you straighten up in your chair. "Sorry." Mrs. Sokoloff gives you one final stern look and then goes back teaching the class, you do your best to pay attention for the rest of class.'
				act 'Wait for the end of the lesson': gs 'gschool_lessonsev2', 'geography'
			end
		elseif RAND(1,3) = 1:
			if pcs_grades >= 80:
				*clr
				'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/sleeping.jpg"></center>'
				'You''re far too tired to pay attention in class today. You don''t even know what the lesson is about, as you keep dozing off.'
				'You''re snapped back to consciousness when you hear Mrs. Sokoloff call your name. Everyone looks at you expectantly, and you realize that you were just asked a question about the topic.'
				'Taking your best guess at what the teacher might be asking, the entire class is shocked as you somehow manage to produce the correct answer, since it must''ve been obvious to everyone that you were sleeping. Mrs. Sokoloff tells you, "Very good, but try and keep your head up during class, if you don''t mind."'
			else
				'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/sleeping.jpg"></center>'
				'You''re far too tired to pay attention in class today. You don''t even know what the lesson is about, since you keep dozing off.'
				'You''re snapped back to consciousness when you hear Mrs. Sokoloff call your name. Everyone is looking at you expectantly, realizing that you were just asked a question about the topic.'
				'You take your best guess at what they might be asking. Some of the other kids snicker when you say something that''s obviously wrong. Mrs. Sokoloff chides you for sleeping in class, and asks for someone else to inform you of the correct answer.'
				'It was an embarrassing experience, but the sudden adrenaline surge helps you to stay awake during the rest of the period.'
			end
			act 'Wait for the end of the lesson': gs 'gschool_lessonsev2', 'geography'
		elseif RAND(1,2) = 1:
			*clr
			'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/sleeping.jpg"></center>'
			'You''re far too tired to pay attention in class today. You don''t even know what the lesson is about, as you keep dozing off.'
			'All of a sudden you hear Mrs. Sokoloff loudly say, "There''s a surprise test in 10 minutes. Until then you''re free to do whatever you want."'
			'You panic as you''ve not prepared anything and you begin to franticly flip through the pages as fast as possible trying to remember the content as the clock ticks down faster and faster.'
			'You''re awoken by the sheer horror of that you''re even haunted by the geography lessons in your dreams.'
			act 'Leave class': gt 'gschool_lessons', 'short_break'
		else
			*clr
			'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/sleeping.jpg"></center>'
			'Mrs. Sokoloff is having a lesson about exotic places around the world. You close your eyes as you fantasize about these places.'
			'Suddenly you stand in front of a group of people with a globe. They tell you that you''re free to spin it and where it stops you''ll get to travel there for free.'
			'Full of enthusiasm you spin it having a hard time deciding when to stop it. When you finally decide stopping it, you notice a familiar name, Pavlovsk. To your dismay you''ve picked your hometown. You desperately look around seeking attention but get no response.'
			'Just as you''re about to speak up and plead with the group of people, you hear the class bell ring waking you shooked up...'
			act 'Leave class': gt 'gschool_lessons', 'short_break'
		end
	end
	act'Play with your phone':
		*clr & cla
		act 'Wait for the end of the lesson': gt 'gschool_lessons', 'short_break'
		pcs_grades -= 1
		'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/phone.jpg"></center>'
		'The lesson is so boring that you have to do something to keep yourself entertained. You take out your phone and begin to play a mobile game, hoping the lesson will be over soon.'
		if RAND(1,4) = 1:
			*clr & cla
			'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/phone.jpg"></center>'
			'You notice Mrs. Sokoloff looking at you strictly; she must have noticed you''re not paying attention to her class.'
			act 'Put your phone away':
				*clr & cla
				grupvalue[3] += 5
				'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/bored.jpg"></center>'
				'You decide not to aggravate the situation and put your phone away. Mrs. Sokoloff looks at you angerly as she continues the class.'
				act 'Wait for the end of the lesson': gs 'gschool_lessonsev2', 'geography'
			end
			act 'Keep using your phone':
				*clr & cla
				grupvalue[4] +=3
				demerit += 5
				'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/phone.jpg"></center>'
				'Even though Mrs. Sokoloff saw you using your phone, you figure you can get away with it, and just keep browsing the internet. Realizing you still won''t put the phone away, Mrs. Sokoloff walks over to your desk.'
				act 'Take photos under your skirt':
					*clr & cla
					pcs_horny += 10
					'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/upskirtselfie.jpg"></center>'
					'You decide to have some fun with your teacher, and quickly move the phone between your legs and snap some photos under your skirt as you see Mrs. Sokoloff walking towards your desk.'
					'When the teacher arrives at your desk, she tells you, "And what could you be doing on your phone that''s more important than paying attention in class, Miss. <<$pcs_lastname>>? Hand it over."'
					'"Wouldn''t you like to know!" you tease. You hand over your phone, the screen still on, with the last picture you took still on the screen of the phone.'
					'Mrs. Sokoloff looks at what''s on the screen having her face color become bright red as she turns the screen off.'
					'She walks back to her desk muttering to herself, "I don''t know what''s wrong with the youth today, who in their right mind would take such photos."'
					'By her desk she tells you, "Miss. <<$pcs_lastname>> you can have your phone back after we''ve had a talk after the lesson."'
					act 'Wait for the end of the lesson': gs 'gschool_lessonsev2', 'geography'
				end
				act 'Put the phone between your boobs':
					*clr & cla
					demerit += 5
					'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/nophone.jpg"></center>'
					'You deftly shove the phone in your bra, and smile fiendishly as you see the indecisiveness on Mrs. Sokoloff''s face.'
					'You pretend it''s a perfectly normal place to store your phone, and use your cute voice as you tell her, "Is there a problem, Mrs. Sokoloff? Go ahead, take my phone if you don''t think I should have it." You thrust your chest forward as you encourage her, giving her a nice view of your ample cleavage - the outline of your phone very visible through the fabric.'
					'Mrs. Sokoloff is at first completely flabbergasted by your move, and just as you think she''ll admit defeat she reaches for it without any hesitation. She simply returns to the front of the class and continues the lesson.'
					'You sit there in awe by her actions, she called your bluff without even blinking.'
					act 'Wait for the end of the lesson': gs 'gschool_lessonsev2', 'geography'
				end
				act 'Hand over the phone':
					*clr & cla
					grupvalue[4] -=3
					grupvalue[3] += 3
					'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/school/classroom/bored.jpg"></center>'
					'Wow, Mrs. Sokoloff called your bluff. You decide it''s not worth the conflict, and silently hand your phone to Mrs. Sokoloff.'
					'As she walk back to the front of the class, she say, "I''m holding onto your phone for now, Mrs. <<$pcs_lastname>>. You can have it back after class."'
					act 'Wait for the end of the lesson': gs 'gschool_lessonsev2', 'geography'
				end
			end
		end
	end
end

